tickets.title: Cannot login to my account
tickets.content: I've been trying to log into my account for the past hour but keep getting an 'invalid credentials' error. I'm sure my password is correct because I have it saved. Can you help me reset my password or check if there's an issue with my account?

tickets.title: Payment not processed
tickets.content: I made a payment yesterday using my credit card but it hasn't been reflected in my account yet. The money was deducted from my bank but the service is still showing as unpaid. Transaction ID is TXN123456. Please help resolve this urgently.

tickets.title: Feature request - Dark mode
tickets.content: I love your application but I really need a dark mode option. I use the app late at night and the bright screen hurts my eyes. Many modern apps have this feature and it would greatly improve user experience. Please consider adding this in the next update.

tickets.title: App crashes on startup
tickets.content: Every time I try to open the application, it crashes immediately. I've tried uninstalling and reinstalling but the problem persists. I'm using iOS 17.2 on iPhone 14. This started happening after the latest update. Please fix this bug.

tickets.title: Forgot password - need reset
tickets.content: I forgot my password and need to reset it. When I click on 'Forgot Password' link, I don't receive any email. I've checked my spam folder too. My email address is correct in the system. Can you manually send me a password reset link?

tickets.title: Slow performance on Android
tickets.content: The app is extremely slow on my Android device. It takes forever to load pages and sometimes freezes completely. I have a Samsung Galaxy S21 with good internet connection. Other apps work fine. Please optimize the Android version.

tickets.title: Refund request for subscription
tickets.content: I was charged for an annual subscription but I only wanted the monthly plan. I signed up two days ago and haven't used any premium features yet. Can I get a refund and switch to the monthly subscription instead?

tickets.title: Data sync issues between devices
tickets.content: My data is not syncing between my phone and laptop. Changes I make on one device don't appear on the other. I'm logged into the same account on both devices. Is there a sync button I'm missing or is this a known issue?

tickets.title: Security concern - unauthorized access
tickets.content: I noticed some activity on my account that I didn't perform. Someone seems to have accessed my account from a different location. I'm worried about security. Please help me secure my account and investigate this unauthorized access.

tickets.title: Cannot download purchased content
tickets.content: I purchased a premium content pack yesterday but I can't download it. When I click the download button, nothing happens. My internet connection is working fine. The purchase shows in my order history. Please help me access my purchased content.
